                            <comment id="85149" author="pwebb" created="Thu, 15 Nov 2012 15:37:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Some work had been done to provide basic portlet support (see &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SWF-1550&quot; title=&quot;Upgrade portlet support to JSF 2.0&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SWF-1550&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SWF-1550&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;). We don&apos;t support AJAX functionality as yet in a portlet environment. Community patches would be welcome.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
